asset.hookText: If your WindTunnel Air vacuum is suddenly shutting off or overheating, we can help. Your vacuum is likely overheating and turning itself off due to a clog somewhere in the system. This simple, fast tutorial will walk you through some steps you can take to get your Hoover Air vacuum back in great condition!
